<h2>Fees</h2>
<p>Cégep Heritage College is tuition free for Quebec residents. There is an application fee of $30, a file review of $30, and an evaluation fee of $50 per course competency or group of competencies, up to a maximum of $600 for an AEC and $1,200 for a DEC. Regular course fees may apply if an applicant must take a course. </p>
<hr />
<h2>Application</h2>
<p>
    To be admitted to Cégep Heritage College, applicants must meet the admission requirements of the program and provide proof of their Quebec residency status. Please contact the RAC Advisor for more information about admission requirements and procedure.
</p>
